caption:
#7 most popular post of 2023. If you're celebrating today, I hope you have a wonderful day. If you need some community, we're hosting a holiday dinner for members of the @callinghome.co family cyclebreakers club tonight at 6 PM ET. Come and meet other people like you who may be lonely this holiday season or looking to vent/ask for advice.

To join, go to callinghome.co and join the family cyclebreakers club. After you join, click on the topics page and find the Bonus: Help For The Holidays section. You'll find the registration for the Family Dinner. We'd love to have you.
